{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_02_02",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 2話 ずっと、こうしていられたら",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuu",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年7月24日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――July 24‚ 2017",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.1866665999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～っ……疲れた～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "sigh… I'm tired…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-15.m4a",
      "text": "もう？　「疲れた」なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? \"Tired\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-11.m4a",
      "text": "仕事じゃ聞いたことないのに。どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've never heard you say that at work. What happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "体は疲れてない。でも、神経を使う\nそれももの凄く使う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not physical exhaustion. It's the mental strain…\nAnd it's a lot of strain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-01.m4a",
      "text": "どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-17.m4a",
      "text": "私達、普通に仲良く遊んでるだけだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're just having fun together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2371686473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がはしゃぎ過ぎるからだぞ\nあんなに大声を出すなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because you get too excited‚ Mana.\nDon't shout so loudly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-02.m4a",
      "text": "無言でジェットコースターに乗ってる人の方が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think people who ride the roller coaster in silence",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "かえって目立つと思うけどな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "actually stand out more‚ you know~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それだけじゃない。他のアトラクションでも騒いでたろ\n目立ち過ぎる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just that. You were noisy on other attractions too.\nYou stand out too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "誰かに写真を撮られてSNSにアップされたら\nどうするんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if someone takes a picture and posts it on the SNS?\nWhat will you do then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-26.m4a",
      "text": "別に撮らせたらいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ what's wrong with letting them take pictures?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ。そんなことになったら、マスコミに\n長瀬麻奈が変な男と交際してるとか書かれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that's not okay. If that happens‚ the media might write…\nthat Mana Nagase is dating a weird guy or something…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-14.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、この人は変な男なんかじゃありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ this person is not a weird guy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "――ってはっきり言うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "- I will say it clearly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺を擁護してくれ、と言ってる訳じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not asking you to defend me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんはやっぱり心配し過ぎだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ you really worry too much~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
      "text": "気遣いは嬉しいけどさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I appreciate your concern‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_tired-03.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく今は二人で遊びに来たんだから、楽しもうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "since we've come here to have fun together‚ let's enjoy ourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりの休日なのは、私だけじゃなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a rare day off‚ not just for me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}くんも同じでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but for {user} too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "今日はアイドルとか、マネージャーとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ we're not idols or managers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-05.m4a",
      "text": "そーいうの一切なし！　OK？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No such roles! Okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（……アイドルとマネージャーじゃないなら）\n（今、俺達は、どんな関係なんだ……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If we're not idols or managers…）\n（What kind of relationship are we in right now…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（クラスメイト？　いや、ただのクラスメイト同士で）\n（二人きりで遊園地に行くのか？　分からない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Classmates? No‚ just classmates going to an amusement park together…）\n（Just the two of us?… I don't know…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん！　聞いてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}! Are you listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん、考え事して聞いてなかった。何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry‚ I was lost in thought. What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_enter-01.m4a",
      "text": "私、次あそこに行きたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to go to that place next!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "お化け屋敷……？　大丈夫なのか？\nここのは本格的って聞いてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The haunted house…? Are you sure about that?\nI heard it's really scary here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前でしょ～？\n私、お化けとか幽霊とか、全然平気だし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course~!\nI'm totally fine with ghosts and stuff!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-08.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーっ！　ひゃーっ！　ちょっ、待って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! Hya! Wait‚ wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
